title: How to Make a Carrot Nut Cake

steps.headline: In a large bowl combine flour, baking soda, baking powder and salt.
In the center of the mixture create a well with a spoon.
Add the beaten eggs, oil and sugar to the center of the well.
Beat the mixture on high speed,for two minutes or until completely blended.
Add carrots, raisins, nuts and cinnamon and stir into the cake batter.
Pour mixture into the buttered tube cake pan.
Cool for 15 minutes prior to removing cake from pan.

text: Preheat oven to 300ºF/150ºC.  Butter one tube cake pan.  In a large bowl combine flour, baking soda, baking powder and salt.  In the center of the mixture create a well with a spoon.  Add the beaten eggs, oil and sugar to the center of the well.  Beat the mixture on high speed,for two minutes or until completely blended.  Add carrots, raisins, nuts and cinnamon and stir into the cake batter.  Pour mixture into the buttered tube cake pan.  Bake 1 hour and 15 minutes minutes.  Cool for 15 minutes prior to removing cake from pan.  Finished.
